  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cozy strategy game with good lofi hip hop music. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2423780/extras/6a770cd0ce08801a66a82a54e1d474f7.poster.avif?t=1769351607\" width=400 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2423780/extras/6a770cd0ce08801a66a82a54e1d474f7.webm?t=1769351607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2423780/extras/6a770cd0ce08801a66a82a54e1d474f7.mp4?t=1769351607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are just chilling when a secret door opens to your basement. But there are lots of monsters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your father's Teleport Sword. Find out where he disappeared long ago.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to reach the 100th floor and find out the surprising truth?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Turn-based strategy battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Obtain special abilities, like the Teleport Attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Infinite replayability + 50 hand-designed levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Customization:  Buy new skins, outfits and swords</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find out the story about your father's disappearance and the monsters' origin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Good Lofi hip hop music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ideal to play while listening to something</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here you can see a penguin chilling and listening to the game's good music:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2423780/extras/407aed51791c98ece34fe78af80cbe98.apng?t=1769351607\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2423780/extras/407aed51791c98ece34fe78af80cbe98.poster.avif?t=1769351607\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cozy strategy game with good lofi hip hop music. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2423780/extras/6a770cd0ce08801a66a82a54e1d474f7.poster.avif?t=1769351607\" width=400 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2423780/extras/6a770cd0ce08801a66a82a54e1d474f7.webm?t=1769351607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2423780/extras/6a770cd0ce08801a66a82a54e1d474f7.mp4?t=1769351607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are just chilling when a secret door opens to your basement. But there are lots of monsters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your father's Teleport Sword. Find out where he disappeared long ago.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to reach the 100th floor and find out the surprising truth?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Turn-based strategy battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Obtain special abilities, like the Teleport Attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Infinite replayability + 50 hand-designed levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Customization:  Buy new skins, outfits and swords</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find out the story about your father's disappearance and the monsters' origin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Good Lofi hip hop music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ideal to play while listening to something</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here you can see a penguin chilling and listening to the game's good music:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2423780/extras/407aed51791c98ece34fe78af80cbe98.apng?t=1769351607\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2423780/extras/407aed51791c98ece34fe78af80cbe98.poster.avif?t=1769351607\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span></p>",
